'''纳坦兹'''（[[波斯语|波斯语]]：'''{{lang|fa|نطنز}}'''）是[[伊朗|伊朗]][[伊斯法罕省|伊斯法罕省]]的一个镇。伊朗在該地設有納坦茲核設施，占地10万平方米，是伊朗最大的铀浓缩设施<ref>{{cite news |title=发生“神秘”事故的伊朗纳坦兹核设施，是个怎样的存在 |url=https://www.jfdaily.com/news/detail?id=265692 |publisher=上觀新聞}}</ref>。2020年7月2日，纳坦兹铀浓缩設施的离心机生产车间发生火灾和爆炸<ref>{{cite web|url=https://apnews.com/50c3e7f6445ae99def6bdc65fbce6c42|title=Analysts: Fire at Iran nuclear site hit centrifuge facility|website=Associated Press|date=2 July 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/02/us/politics/iran-explosion-nuclear-centrifuges.html|title=Mysterious Explosion and Fire Damage Iranian Nuclear Enrichment Facility|website=The New York Times|date=2 July 2020}}</ref>。一个名为 "祖国猎豹 "（Cheetahs of the Homeland）的组织声称对此次袭击负责<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/report-israeli-cyberattack-caused-iran-nuclear-site-fire-f35s-hit-missile-base/|title=Report: Israeli cyberattack caused Iran nuclear site fire, F35s hit missile base|website=The Times of Israel|date=3 July 2020}}</ref>。一些伊朗官员表示，该事件可能是通過网络破坏造成的<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-iran-nuclear-natanz/iran-threatens-retaliation-after-what-it-calls-possible-cyber-attack-on-nuclear-site-idUSKBN2441VY |title=Iran threatens retaliation after what it calls possible cyber attack on nuclear site |website=Reuters |date=3 July 2020 }}</ref>。2021年4月11日，纳坦兹核设施电力系统出现问题<ref>{{cite news |title=伊朗纳坦兹核设施“出事” |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-04/12/c_1211106465.htm}}</ref>。伊朗政府聲稱是遭到以色列恐怖襲擊<ref>{{cite news |title=伊朗外长指责以色列破坏伊朗核设施 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-04/12/c_1127321576.htm}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=英媒：伊朗称纳坦兹核设施遭“核恐怖主义”袭击 |url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-04-12/doc-ikmxzfmk6295291.shtml}}</ref>。一名官員表示有數以千計用於提煉核物質的機器被毀壞或受損<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-56734657 |title=Iran Natanz nuclear site suffered major damage, official says |publisher=BBC |date=2021-04-13}}</ref>。

